This volume contains the proceedings of the Thirty-First Annual ACM/IEEE Symposium on Logic in Computer Science (LICS) held at Columbia University in New York City from July 5 to July 8, 2016. LICS is an annual international forum on theoretical and practical topics in computer science that relate to logic. The first LICS symposium was held in 1986, and LICS 2016 marks the thirtieth anniversary of that event.